# abs-librarian ignore rules
# Works like .gitignore: patterns match filenames/paths relative to the Audiobooks root.
# Trailing / = directories only. Lines starting with # are comments.

# ── Tool files (never touch these) ───────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/
.audiobooksignore
REORGANIZATION_GLOSSARY.md

# ── NAS/sync system directories ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.stfolder
.Recycle.Bin/

# ── Protected content ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Encrypted/

# ── Audiobookshelf working directories ───────────────────────────────────────
_NeedsReview/
_non-audiobook/
